message:
We are so grateful for Summit Live. There is no other conference we've attended that has such a diverse group of people willing to discuss child trafficking. From Tech, Content Creators, Law Enforcement to Hollywood, people come together here to share their expertise and learn from one another. We've had people non stop asking questions, learning and then asking how they can help spread awareness about ChildTrafficking. 
Thank you Ryan Anderson Bell #HelpERASE #SummitLive
